name: InvalidKeySpecException
comment: This is the exception for invalid key specifications.

constructors.name: InvalidKeySpecException

Constructs an InvalidKeySpecException with no detail message. A
 detail message is a String that describes this particular
 exception.

constructors.name: InvalidKeySpecException
constructors.comment:
Creates a {@code InvalidKeySpecException} with the specified cause
 and a detail message of {@code (cause==null ? null : cause.toString())}
 (which typically contains the class and detail message of
 {@code cause}).
